                        Phone: (619) 533-7000<br>
                        Email:&nbsp;<a href="mailto:tickets@sdopera.com" data-mce-href="mailto:tickets@sdopera.com"></a><a>tickets@sdopera.com</a><br>
                        Hours: Mon-Fri, 8:30am to 4:30pm</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>